abstract: United States defeats Cuba, 12-10, in the baseball semifinals at the Pan American Games in Guadalajara, Mexico.
snippet: The United States beat the 10-time defending champion Cuba, 12-10, in the baseball semifinals at the Pan American Games in Guadalajara, Mexico.
